job.title: Sr. Frontend Engineer
job.description:
We are looking for a Senior Frontend Engineer to join Quansight Labs and our 
mission of supporting the PyData open-source ecosystem. 
As a Senior Frontend Engineer, you will lead our internal web-related projects 
and contribute to the community-driven open-source projects supported by 
Quansight Labs. We are seeking great engineers who are passionate about web 
development, open source, accessibility and who possess a collaborative and 
community-first mindset.
